<subSubSection pageId="278" pageNumber="883" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="278.[1396,2603,726,1312]" pageId="278" pageNumber="883">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[1396,1631,963,997]" pageId="278" pageNumber="883">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
The Ethiopian Amphibious Rat is thought to be terrestrial and semiaquatic.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
